cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.NE 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.RO (Robotics) - The paper focuses on implementing bodily awareness in soft robots, which falls under the domain of robotics. 
2. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper proposes a method that uses a combination of autoencoders and recurrent neural networks, which are commonly used in AI research. 
3. cs.CV (Computer Vision) - The paper discusses the mapping of internal sensory signals to visual information, which involves computer vision techniques. 
4. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The proposed method involves the use of machine learning algorithms to enable the soft robot to learn to imagine its motion. 
5. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) - The paper uses a recurrent neural network as part of the proposed method, which falls under the domain of neural computing.
